{"root":{"data":{"id":"djv2npu2m9k0","created":1783705019800,"text":"向量数据库"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv2nu75j7s0","created":1783705029299,"text":"什么是向量数据库","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-76.50000066797884,"y":-152.50000099363626},"priority":"1"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv5r4u1ap40","created":1783713750872,"text":"结构","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999995936037,"y":-132.49999989230542}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv5rqnuvvk0","created":1783713798388,"text":"id"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv5s8f64y00","created":1783713837045,"text":"向量坐标"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv5sb0x7fc0","created":1783713842713,"text":"元数据"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv5sp7390o0","created":1783713873561,"text":"场景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv5ssc7te00","created":1783713880402,"text":"存FAQ"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv5sz3ync80","created":1783713895140,"text":"标准问题和答案存在向量数据库中，且可以不调用LLM,不会产生token费用，查询速度又快","layout_right_offset":{"x":77.49999993700862,"y":-12.499999989840092}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv5vuotduo0","created":1783714120610,"text":"向量是“标准问题”生成的","layout_right_offset":{"x":71.24999994208872,"y":-18.74999998476028}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv5svixyao0","created":1783713887339,"text":"存长文本","layout_right_offset":{"x":1.2499999989840944,"y":33.74999997256856}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv5wnk1quo0","created":1783714183448,"text":"向量是“文章段落正文”（长文切片）生成"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv2nzxbceg0","created":1783705041764,"text":"如何工作","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-43.0000075348396,"y":-36.500002116100404},"expandState":"expand","priority":"2","progress":null,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv2og9nsxc0","created":1783705077339,"text":"数据向量化","layout_right_offset":{"x":370.74999965395455,"y":40.74999984766987},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv313n7lyg0","created":1783706068595,"text":"利用训练好的大模型生成向量","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":343.74999972060345,"y":-1.2499999989839807}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv2ol7rt5c0","created":1783705088109,"text":"构建索引","layout_right_offset":{"x":360.7499996620829,"y":50.74999976503591},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv31o6q01k0","created":1783706113310,"text":"近似最近邻（ANN）","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":322.4999997378752,"y":1.2499999989839807}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv32ubeouo0","created":1783706205018,"text":"HNSW：构建“智能导航图”","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":398.74999967589974,"y":3.749999996952056}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv32z4jik00","created":1783706215487,"text":"IVF：建立“智能目录”","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":389.9999996830122,"y":23.749999980696202}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv33l2x55k0","created":1783706263278,"text":"PQ：实施“向量压缩”","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":367.4999997012999,"y":39.99999996748841}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv3413s6hs0","created":1783706298159,"text":"IVF_PQ索引","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":328.74999973279546,"y":39.99999996748852}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv2opqybzs0","created":1783705097976,"text":"计算相似度","layout_right_offset":{"x":403.2499996275394,"y":110.24999967197186},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3b76ln080","created":1783706859939,"text":"余弦相似度","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":267.4999997825787,"y":12.499999989840035}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3byrx96g0","created":1783706920001,"text":"场景：处理文本、语义搜索（如RAG问答）","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":446.2499996372926,"y":-44.99999996342467}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3i4hetww0","created":1783707402612,"text":"用时钟理解，两个向量靠的越近余弦值越接近1，\n就约相似","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":632.4999994859102,"y":-1.2499999989839807}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv3biufc4g0","created":1783706885324,"text":"欧氏距离","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":261.2499997876587,"y":36.24999997053635}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3c7ev35c0","created":1783706938803,"text":"场景：处理图像、音频或推荐系统（向量模长有意义））","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":534.9999995651576,"y":-54.999999955296516}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv3boy3vns0","created":1783706898608,"text":"点积","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":261.2499997876589,"y":42.49999996545648}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3cdb9cog0","created":1783706951646,"text":"追求极致的查询速度使用点积，但前提是必须确保所有向量都已归一化。","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":573.749999533662,"y":4.999999995936037}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv3lnnc02g0","created":1783707679421,"text":"召回率","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":372.4999996972365,"y":166.24999986487398}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3oq28m7c0","created":1783707919768,"text":"召回率 = 索引实际找到的“真近邻”数量 / 理论上暴力搜索应该找到的“真近邻”总数","layout_right_offset":{"x":699.9999994310465,"y":8.749999992888092}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv3u3zk0uw0","created":1783708341902,"text":"相邻重叠","layout_right_offset":{"x":298.7499997571788,"y":27.499999977648372}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv3u88hphc0","created":1783708351149,"text":"一段语义被拆分成了两段文档分块，导致相似度变低进而影响召回率","layout_right_offset":{"x":541.2499995600779,"y":-2.499999997968075}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djv4g3rritc0","created":1783710065442,"text":"向量数据库返回的内容太大，实际问题很小怎么办","layout_mind_offset":{"x":678.0000095519157,"y":646.0000091010876},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv4hcgcb800","created":1783710162707,"text":"影响：假设返回512大小的切片，答案只占20个token。\n稀释了上下文： 导致 LLM 在合成答案时引入不必要的细节或偏离焦点。\n增加了成本： 您为这 492 个不必要的 Token 付费。","layout_right_offset":{"x":928.0000130740092,"y":94.00000132430682}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djv4j99wezc0","created":1783710312515,"text":"解决方案","layout_right_offset":{"x":528.0000074386603,"y":50.00000070441854}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djv4jjnt8n40","created":1783710335124,"text":"A. 重叠分块 (Chunk Overlap)\n思想： 分块之间保留一小段重复内容（比如 10%）。\n作用： 确保重要的句子或段落的上下文不会在分块的边界处被切断，保证语义的完整性。\n\nB. 父子分块（Parent-Child Chunking）\n思想： 存储两个版本的文档块：\n小块（Child Chunk）： 用于检索（例如 128 个 Token，保证高精度）。\n大块（Parent Chunk）： 用于生成（例如 512 个 Token，提供足够上下文）。\n\n\n流程： 检索时用小块找到最相关的向量 =》找到其对应的 512 Token 的大块 =》将大块送给 LLM。\n效果： 结合了小块的高检索精度和大块的高质量上下文。\n\nC. 后处理重排（Post-Processing / Re-ranking）\n思想： 向量搜索很快，但可能粗糙。\n流程： 向量数据库先返回 Top-20 的结果 =》使用一个更强、更慢的重排模型（Reranker，通常是小型 BERT 模型）对这 20 个结果进行二次评估=》选出真正相关的 Top-3。\n作用： 去除向量搜索引入的假阳性（False Positives），大幅提高最终精度。\n\nD. 元数据过滤（Metadata Filtering）\n思想： 在搜索时就排除无关的文档。\n应用： 如果你知道用户在问**“2023 年”**的事情，可以在查询时告诉向量数据库：“只搜索 年份=2023 的文档块。” 这能瞬间缩小搜索范围，提高精准度。","layout_right_offset":{"x":1191.99998524731,"y":112.00000116933472}},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}